title: Tannehill helps Dolphins improve to 2-0 under coach Campbell
text:
> Texas Tannehill helps Dolphins improve to 2-0 under coach Campbell Houston Texans quarterback Brian Hoyer (7) looks to pass the ball during the first half of an NFL football game against the Miami Dolphins, Sunday, Oct. 25, 2015 in Miami Gardens, Fla. The Dolphins defeated the Texans 44-26. (AP Photo/Wilfredo Lee) The most compelling, sharable stories from across the web.
